  <brief_title>Treatment of Spastic Equinovarus Foot After Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment of Spastic Equinovarus Foot After Stroke. Efficacy: Association Between Ankle Foot Orthosis and Botulinum Toxin A (BTA) Injection</official_title>
